document.full_text: american nick watney fired an eight-under-par 64 to grab the first round lead at the players championship on thursday while an injured tiger woods limped out of the event after just nine holes.
document.title: watney grabs lead at players, tiger withdraws
lines_and_colors: american nick watney fired an eight-under-par 64 to grab the first round lead at the players championship on thursday while an injured tiger woods limped out of the event after just nine holes.
